OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith patchy rain, mainly across
OL,7,FArgyll. Drier but rather cloudy this
OL,8,Fafternoon, but still some rain at
OL,9,Ftimes across Argyll. Some afternoon
OL,10,Fbrightness possible in the south.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening and overnight
OL,13,Fwill be cloudy with some patchy light
OL,14,Frain, this mainly across Argyll. Some
OL,15,Fmisty low cloud along the coast. Light
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
