OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FSome drizzly rain across
OL,6,FArgyll in the morning. Otherwise it
OL,7,Fwill be dry with cloud thinning to
OL,8,Fgive some sunshine during the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,12,Fwith some sunshine on Thursday
OL,13,Falthough cloudier across Argyll. Dry
OL,14,Fwith plenty of sunshine on Friday and
OL,15,FSaturday. Perhaps a few showers
OL,16,FSaturday. Becoming very warm or hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
